{
  "stem": "3360.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Another thing that I have to-- that I was thinking of right now that is amazing, that when you heard all these things said about Jews, and at every corner then, what had been done.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "At just about every street corner, they had was a, a scandal sheet by Julius Streicher, one of the most outrageous, vicious Nazis-- Julius Streicher.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "S-- Julius and Streicher, S-T-R-E-I-C-H-E-R.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "the, the publication-- so-called.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "S-T-U umlaut R-M-E-R.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was in a-- not a kiosk-type setting, but it was-- it was enclosed for people to, to see it and to read the headlines.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I think every headline that they ever had-- and they changed it at least weekly-- showed a, you know, the, the, the, the-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] a sketch of what you'd call the ugliest Jew-- what Arafat looks like, as a matter of fact.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I shouldn't say that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But, you know, he looks like what they used to picture as a very ugly Jew.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He Is sort of the personification, you know, the terrible nose, and the-- and whatever, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There's half, half, half-laugh, or whatever it is, on the face.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then the worst stories about Jews, you know, what kind of rats they are, vermin, and whatever-- the worst kind of things.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that was at every-- just about every-- at many street corners.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The other thing that you had, every weekend, the Nazis would collect money.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So the SA, the brown shirts, would be out in the street.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they would be jangling there-- like the good Salvation Army does-- they would be jangling their cans, you know, for people to put money in there.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
